Phase 1: Project Setup & Common Infrastructure
✅ Backend (Spring Boot):
 Set up Spring Boot project (use Spring Initializr)

Dependencies: Spring Web, Spring Data JPA, Spring Security, MySQL or PostgreSQL, Lombok, JWT (for auth)

 Set up database connection

 Create base project structure (controllers, services, repositories, models, DTOs)

 Implement JWT-based authentication & authorization

 Create user model (id, username, email, password, roles, etc.)

✅ Frontend (React):
 Set up React app with Vite or CRA

 Add routing (React Router)

 Create Auth Context for login/logout state

 Build login, signup, and protected routes

 Axios setup for API calls with token handling